'''Orbital Shipyard 1321''' was one of the [[Fondor Shipyards/Legends|Fondor Shipyards]]. In [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]], its foreman was [[Creed Mitsun]] and it was constructing the ''[[Amerce]]''. It was destroyed in the [[Battle of Fondor]] when [[Yorik-et|coralskippers]] rammed it.

